recipe.label: Apple Crisp
ingredientLines: Apples, cinnamon, brown sugar, butter and oats? welcome to the essential ingredients of the apple crisp

, one of the most simple and easy of apple desserts. to make an apple crisp one layer's sliced peeled apples that have been tossed with lemon juice and vanilla in a baking pan, then tops the apples with a mixture of brown sugar, butter, cinnamon and oats. it's the crunchy topping that makes the apple crisp "crisp".
